{"tid":2327728,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"周庭申請保釋等候上訴遭拒 張慧玲今頒裁決理由 指判監10個月以儆效尤絕非明顯過重","createTime":"2020-12-16T09:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T10:27:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"eba4084acef328bee2807515468ad39bb869ac43","tid":2327728,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:22:29.000Z","msg":"前香港眾志成員黃之鋒、周庭及林朗彥因去年6.21煽惑包圍警總，分別被判囚7至13個半月，其中判監10個月的周庭，上周三向高院申請保釋等候上訴，但遭拒絕。法官張慧玲今頒下裁決理由，直指周庭作為公眾人物，以領導者角色積極犯案，又謂本案案情非常嚴重，原審裁判官王詩麗判處10個月即時監禁的刑罰以儆效尤，絕非明顯過重，並無犯錯。<br />\n<br />\n自上月23日認罪答辯後一直還柙的周庭，今沒有到庭領取判詞。其代表律師於上周三聆訊後透露，周庭對裁決感到失望及遺憾，並謂她目前身體狀況欠佳，仍在努力適應監獄生活，又呼籲牆外手足繼續關注在囚人士。<br />\n<br />\n對於上訴理據聲言原審裁判官王詩麗錯誤採納上訴庭雙學三子「黃之鋒案」的判刑原則，指該案非法集結牽涉暴力，涉及破壞社會安寧或威脅破壞社會安寧，行為有挑撥性，與本案未經批准集結罪的控罪要旨不同，強調未經批准集結獲《基本法》賦予的遊行集會自由保障，非法集結則不會。<br />\n<br />\n張官於判詞反駁指，裁判官「借鏡」黃之鋒案的判刑因素並無不妥，更絕非犯下任何原則性錯誤，強調未經批准集結罪雖然並無判刑指引，但法庭必須考慮案情，以作恰當判刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201216/ES7NQP5B2BFARPDTYRNVLT3P2U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201216%2FES7NQP5B2BFARPDTYRNVLT3P2U%2F&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU4nMh2OwnA7FCi%2BsKpr4SDY%3D&h=a4707dc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201216%2FES7NQP5B2BFARPDTYRNVLT3P2U%2F&h=1ee9f5fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201216/ES7NQP5B2BFARPDTYRNVLT3P2U/</a>"},{"pid":"49001bfaa232efafc2d585420a16e786812d247b","tid":2327728,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd616832dd36b19ce5ac2b2288d96f2748e8b08","tid":2327728,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:23:09.000Z","msg":"上訴理據還包括裁判官錯誤地將兩項控罪分期執行。張官指以本案情況，裁判官認為兩罪須分期執行，或有商榷之處；惟她認為，裁判官在考慮整體刑期後判處10個月的監禁，不算明顯過重。由於上訴方無法證明有極高或合理的上訴成功機會，故即使周庭在上訴聆訊時可能已服畢全部或大部份刑期，拒讓她保釋外出亦不會構成不公。"},{"pid":"82e4692718c1487e35d88ad3a7264ab75614f238","tid":2327728,"uid":83052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:23:36.000Z","msg":"分享笑話一則：香港法治"},{"pid":"2713626dff0f2e13d7615503685bfcd0df94afb6","tid":2327728,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:25:41.000Z","msg":"裁決理由全文: <a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=132454&amp;currpage=T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fju%2Fju_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D132454%26currpage%3DT&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU4nMh2OwnA7FCi%2BsKpr4SDY%3D&h=3f00a8a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=132454&amp;currpage=T</a>"},{"pid":"8473d879177ff4dbd8fdcd5c7f075899de8c5ec0","tid":2327728,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:30:52.000Z","msg":"法官不認同申請方稱原審裁判官犯錯，並指「判處即時監禁，以儆效尤是正確判刑」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E5%91%A8%E5%BA%AD%E7%94%B3%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92-%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98-%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83-%E6%87%89%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E7%9B%A3%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A5%E5%84%86%E6%95%88%E5%B0%A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E7%2594%25B3%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%2583%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%2590%2586%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E7%259B%25A3%25E7%25A6%2581%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%2584%2586%25E6%2595%2588%25E5%25B0%25A4%2F&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU4nMh2OwnA7FCi%2BsKpr4SDY%3D&h=d36cb1c7\" data-ef-ur